summary:
I've worked as an English teacher for ten years in Argentina. I have experience in teaching all ages, from four-year-olds to adults in both public and private schools and all my employers or principals have congratulated me on my responsibility, creativity and good atmosphere in my classes. 
I have led courses of English as a foreign language, international exams preparation, English for travellers and the subjects History and Intercultural Studies in English at a teacher training college. 
I show good skills of team leadership, which I developed working as an English Coordinator in two different schools.
